episodes.title: First Coast Connect:  “The Psychology of Cults”
episodes.description:
https://news.wjct.org/show/first-coast-connect/2025-10-06/on-tuesdays-show-ask-the-mayor

We sit down with Jacksonville Mayor Donna Deegan to discuss the latest city business — from a highly contentious budget battle to accusations of wasteful spending to the abrupt departure of her chief administrative officer. She also takes your calls and questions.

Guest:

Jacksonville Mayor Donna Deegan.
